{
  "stem": "9538.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No sooner did you have them repaired than stones flew through them again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And lots of atrocities went on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my father's business and everybody else's business came to a standstill because people were afraid to deal with Jewish-- Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Financially, it became very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we still stayed in our-- in my-- in our house, and people came who tried to flee over the Dutch border.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, my parents took them in, you know, Jewish people from other parts of Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They tried to, at night, to cross the borders, and they waited for a few days, and it was convenient for them to slip across and my parents--",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very difficult.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very few made it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They got arrested and were sent to this prison in-- in-- in my hometown.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was quite-- in Berlin, we didn't notice it so much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were in an enclave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were amongst-- I was amongst Jewish boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when you're young, you don't feel it if it doesn't sort of touch you directly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It touched my parents, of course, because, financially and morally, it was-- was-- was-- very-- neighbors who were-- were good to us and-- and friends in the town, they ignored us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to ignore us, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was very, very hard to accept it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, where, for instance, in Berlin, I was a stranger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could go in a shop and-- and-- and up to a certain time still.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But not--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't know who we were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this changed again in 1938.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In November '38, when the Kristallnacht came.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
